'''''Achryson lineolatum''''' is a species of [[longhorn beetle]] in the [[Cerambycinae]] subfamily. It was described by Erichson in 1847.<ref>Bezark, Larry G. [http://plant.cdfa.ca.gov/byciddb/bycidview.asp A Photographic Catalog of the Cerambycidae of the World.] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130827211041/http://plant.cdfa.ca.gov/byciddb/bycidview.asp |date=2013-08-27 }}</ref> It is known from [[Ecuador]], [[Peru]], [[Bolivia]], [[Chile]], and the [[Galapagos Islands]].

